title: The Circus - S01E019
description:
Series 1, Episode 19 of The Circus - the greatest political show on TV with a genuinely unique approach to covering this crazy election.


For some reason the regular uploaders have slowed right down - it's a real shame, I have had to scour all over to find this episode.

Hopefully the regular cappers and HQ uploaders will come back next week, this is essential viewing for every voter as it goes behind the spin and actually shines a light on the candidates
